      "label": "Condition",
      "value": "Recto: The text is incomplete on all sides. The black ink has faded so that the text is unreadable in all but two lines. Several lacunae have damaged the papyrus and the first and last lines consist of traces of letters only. \nVerso: Considering the continuation of a common formula in lines 2-3, it seems that not much of the document\u2019s left and right hand sides is broken off."
